《'''公眾與O·J·辛普森的對決：美國犯罪故事'''》（{{lang-en|''The People v. O. J. Simpson: American Crime Story''}}）為[[FX_(電視頻道)|FX]]{{le|真實犯罪|True crime}}[[詩選劇|詩選劇]]《[[美國犯罪故事|美國犯罪故事]]》（{{lang-en|''American Crime Story''}}）的第一季。由[[史考特·亞歷山大與萊瑞·卡拉蘇斯基|史考特·亞歷山大與萊瑞·卡拉蘇斯基]]開創，於2016年2月2日在FX開播。<ref>{{cite web|title=American Crime Story: The People v. OJ Simpson – Launch|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3qUw4TpLIRI|website=Youtube|publisher=FX Networks|accessdate=2016-08-05|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002021049/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3qUw4TpLIRI|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvline.com/2015/01/18/fargo-season-2-fx-american-crime-story-premiere-date/|title=FX Boss Talks Ronald Reagan's Fargo Season 2 Role, The Americans' Future, Bridge Regrets and More|work={{link-en|TVLine|TVLine}}|first=Vlada|last=Gelman|date=2015-01-18|accessdate=2015-01-18|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613215413/https://tvline.com/2015/01/18/fargo-season-2-fx-american-crime-story-premiere-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/11/12/fx-fxx-premiere-schedule-american-crime-story|title=FX announces premiere dates for American Crime Story and more|publisher=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|first=Megan|last=Daley|date=2015-11-12|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127230417/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/11/12/fx-fxx-premiere-schedule-american-crime-story|dead-url=no}}</ref>本季聚焦於曾轟動全美關注的[[辛普森案|辛普森案]]，並改編{{link-en|傑弗瑞·圖賓|Jeffrey Toobin}}編著的《逃離人生：公眾與O·J·辛普森的對決》（{{lang|en|''The Run of His Life: The People v. O. J. Simpson''}}）一書。<ref name="IGN 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/10/07/fx-orders-american-crime-story-from-american-horror-story-creator|title=FX Orders ''American Crime Story'' From ''American Horror Story'' Creator|date=2014-10-07|website=IGN.com|accessdate=2016-08-05|archive-date=2018-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619140621/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/10/07/fx-orders-american-crime-story-from-american-horror-story-creator|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本季在首播後，獲得影評家廣泛的讚譽，並榮獲[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]22項入圍、最終抱回9座獎項殊榮，同時亦受[[金球獎|金球獎]]、[[英國學術電視獎|英國影藝學院電視獎]]、[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會獎]]、 [[美國製片人協會|美國製片人協會獎]]、[[美國編劇工會獎|美國編劇工會獎]]、{{le|電視評論家協會獎|Television Critics Association Award}}、[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]、{{le|評論家選擇電視獎|Critics' Choice Television Award}}與[[衛星獎|衛星獎]]等多項大獎肯定，[[莎拉·保羅森|莎拉·保羅森]]也在各大獎中斬獲多座女演員獎。

== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
2014年10月7日，[[FX_(電視頻道)|FX]]宣布預訂由[[史考特·亞歷山大與萊瑞·卡拉蘇斯基|史考特·亞歷山大與萊瑞·卡拉蘇斯基]]開發兼製作，《[[整容室|整形春秋]]》、《[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]》、《[[美國恐怖故事|美國恐怖故事]]》與《[[尖叫女王|尖叫女王]]》的{{link-en|布萊德·佛查克|Brad Falchuk}}與[[萊恩·墨菲_(編劇)|萊恩·墨菲]]共同製作的《美國犯罪故事》10集集數。萊恩·墨菲將執導試播集，而{{link-en|妮娜·雅各布森|Nina Jacobson}}與布萊德·辛普森（{{lang|en|Brad Simpson}}）將加入執行製作行列。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/10/07/ryan-murphy-to-tackle-o-j-simpson-case-with-american-crime-story/|title=Ryan Murphy to tackle O.J. Simpson case with 'American Crime Story'|date=2014-10-07|work=娛樂周刊|accessdate=2015-10-30|first=Esther|last=Zuckerman|archive-date=2015-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150118063903/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/10/07/ryan-murphy-to-tackle-o-j-simpson-case-with-american-crime-story/|dead-url=no}}</ref>本劇起初由[[福斯廣播公司|FOX]]開發，後來改由同集團的有線電視網[[FX_(電視頻道)|FX]]製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/fox-developing-shogun-oj-simpson-430050?mobile_redirect=false|title=Fox Developing 'Shogun,' O.J. Simpson Longform Dramas|date=2013-03-20|work=好萊塢報導|first=Lesley|accessdate=2015-10-30|last=Goldberg|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217083055/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/fox-developing-shogun-oj-simpson-430050?mobile_redirect=false}}</ref>

=== 選角 ===
2014年12月9日，[[小庫珀·古丁|小古巴·古汀]]與[[莎拉·保羅森|莎拉·保羅森]]為首兩個加入演員陣容的演員，兩人分別飾演[[O·J·辛普森|O·J·辛普森]]與{{link-en|瑪莎·克拉克|Marcia Clark}}。<ref name="Jr.Paulson1">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/cuba-gooding-jr-sarah-paulson-755630|title=Cuba Gooding, Jr., Sarah Paulson to Star in FX's 'American Crime Story: People v. O.J. Simpson|publisher=好萊塢報導|accessdate=2014-12-09|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306235256/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/cuba-gooding-jr-sarah-paulson-755630}}</ref>隨後，宣布[[大衛·史威默|大衛·史威默]]將飾演[[羅伯特·卡戴珊|羅伯特·卡戴珊]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2014/12/19/david-schwimmer-robert-kardashian-cast-oj-simpson-series-american-crime-story-fx/|first=Michael|accessdate=2015-10-30|last=Ausiello|title=David Schwimmer Joins FX's OJ-Themed American Crime Story as Robert Kardashian|work=TVLine|date=2014-12-19|archive-date=2020-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214062014/https://tvline.com/2014/12/19/david-schwimmer-robert-kardashian-cast-oj-simpson-series-american-crime-story-fx/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年1月，[[約翰·特拉沃爾塔|約翰·屈伏塔]]加入演出陣容飾演{{link-en|勞伯特·沙皮洛|Robert Shapiro (lawyer)}}，並將身兼製作人。<ref name="Travolta1">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/john-travolta-american-crime-story-fx-robert-shapiro-1201394854/|title=John Travolta Lands Lead Role In FX’s ‘American Crime Story’|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|first=Elizabeth|last=Wagmeister|accessdate=2015-01-08|date=2015-01-07|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114232219/https://variety.com/2015/tv/news/john-travolta-american-crime-story-fx-robert-shapiro-1201394854/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年2月，[[寇特尼·B·凡斯|寇特尼·B·凡斯]]加入劇組飾演{{link-en|強尼·卡克倫|Johnnie Cochran}}。<ref name="Vance">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/courtney-b-vance-johnnie-cochran-770665|title=Courtney B. Vance Set as Johnnie Cochran in FX's 'American Crime Story: The People v. O.J. Simpson'|work=好萊塢報導|first=Lesley|last=Goldberg|accessdate=2015-02-07|date=2015-02-05|archive-date=2015-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208085442/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/courtney-b-vance-johnnie-cochran-770665|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年3月，宣布{{link-en|康妮·布里登|Connie Britton}}將飾演配角{{link-en|菲依·雷斯尼克|Faye Resnick}}。<ref name="Britton">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/MrRPMurphy/status/580051701895299072|title=Excited to announce my friend Connie Britton will play Faye Resnick in the upcoming FX miniseries The People v. O.J. Simpson.|work=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|first=Ryan|last=Murphy|accessdate=2015-03-23|date=2015-03-23|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108125456/https://twitter.com/MrRPMurphy/status/580051701895299072|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年4月，宣布[[斯特林·K·布朗|斯特林·K·布朗]]將飾演{{link-en|克里斯多弗·達登|Christopher Darden}}；<ref name="Brown1">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/sterling-brown-cast-christopher-darden-american-crime-story-oj-simpson-1201412083/|title=Sterling K. Brown To Play Christopher Darden in "The People V. O.J. Simpson"|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|date=2015-04-17|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2015-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150420200431/http://deadline.com/2015/04/sterling-brown-cast-christopher-darden-american-crime-story-oj-simpson-1201412083/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[喬丹娜·布魯斯特|喬丹娜·布魯斯特]]則將飾演丹妮絲·布朗；<ref name="Brewster1">{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/04/30/jordana-brewster-american-crime-story|title=Jordana Brewster to play Denise Brown in American Crime Story: The People V. OJ Simpson|work=娛樂周刊|first=Tim|last=Stack|accessdate=2015-04-30|date=2015-04-30|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001055038/https://ew.com/article/2015/04/30/jordana-brewster-american-crime-story/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而{{link-en|肯尼斯·崔|Kenneth Choi}}則將飾演{{link-en|蘭斯·伊藤|Lance Ito}}法官。<ref name="Choi">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/kenneth-choi-judge-ito-people-v-oj-simpson-1201418935/|date=2015-04-30|title=Kenneth Choi To Play Judge Ito In ‘The People V. O.J. Simpson’|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|work=Deadline Hollywood|accessdate=2015-09-19|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114232226/https://deadline.com/2015/04/kenneth-choi-judge-ito-people-v-oj-simpson-1201418935/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年5月，證實[[莎瑪·布萊兒|莎瑪·布萊兒]]將飾演[[克莉絲·詹納|克莉絲·卡戴珊]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/selma-blair-cast-kris-jenner-people-v-oj-simpson-1201424399/|title=Selma Blair To Play Kris Jenner In ‘The People V. O.J. Simpson’|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|work=Deadline Hollywood|accessdate=2015-09-19|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114232155/https://deadline.com/2015/05/selma-blair-cast-kris-jenner-people-v-oj-simpson-1201424399/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年7月，宣布[[納坦·朗|奈森·連恩]]飾演{{link-en|F·李·貝利|F. Lee Bailey}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/nathan-lane-f-lee-bailey-american-crime-story-oj-simpson-trial-series-ryan-murphy-1201475331/|title=Nathan Lane Set As F. Lee Bailey In FX’s O.J. Trial Series ‘American Crime Story’|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2015-07-13|accessdate=2015-09-19|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114232217/https://deadline.com/2015/07/nathan-lane-f-lee-bailey-american-crime-story-oj-simpson-trial-series-ryan-murphy-1201475331/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

