== 評價 ==
[[File:Sarah_Paulson_by_Gage_Skidmore_2.jpg|thumb]]的表現獲得影評家讚賞，並因本劇奪得[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]]]
《美國犯罪故事》獲得了評論家廣泛的好評。於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中，本季獲得97%新鮮度、8.71/10分（75位評論家），評論家共識：「《公眾與O·J·辛普森的對決：美國犯罪故事》以頂尖的編劇、導演與演技來闡明一個基於事實的局部故事 – 並獲得熱烈的反響。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/american_crime_story/s01|title=The People v. O.J. Simpson: American Crime Story|publisher=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|accessdate=2016-02-06|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114235714/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/american_crime_story/s01|dead-url=no}}</ref>於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，本季獲得了90分（滿分100分；43位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/the-people-v-oj-simpson-american-crime-story|title=The People v. O.J. Simpson: American Crime Story - Season 1 Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-02-01|archive-date=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228193615/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/the-people-v-oj-simpson-american-crime-story|dead-url=no}}</ref>

許多評論家非常讚賞演員的演出，特別是[[莎拉·保羅森|莎拉·保羅森]]與{{link-en|寇尼·B·凡斯|Courtney B. Vance}}。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sepinwall|first1=Alan|title=Review: FX's compelling 'The People v. O.J. Simpson: American Crime Story'|url=http://www.hitfix.com/whats-alan-watching/review-fxs-compelling-the-people-v-oj-simpson-american-crime-story|work=[[HitFix|HitFix]]|date=2016-02-01|accessdate=2016-02-03|archive-date=2016-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202091914/http://www.hitfix.com/whats-alan-watching/review-fxs-compelling-the-people-v-oj-simpson-american-crime-story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="FeinbergHR">{{cite web|last1=Fienberg|first1=Dan|title='The People v. O.J. Simpson: American Crime Story': TV Review|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/people-v-oj-simpson-american-856052|work=好萊塢報導|date=2016-01-19|accessdate=2016-02-04|archive-date=2016-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205093922/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/people-v-oj-simpson-american-856052|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Bernstein|first1=Jonathan|title=The People v. OJ Simpson: American Crime Story, review: 'expertly executed entertainment'|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/tv/2016/02/03/the-people-v-oj-simpson-american-crime-story-review-expertly-exe/|work=The Telegraph|date=2016-02-03|accessdate=2016-02-03|archive-date=2020-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011195248/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/tv/2016/02/03/the-people-v-oj-simpson-american-crime-story-review-expertly-exe/|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]〉的丹·范伯格（{{lang|en|Dan Feinberg}}）寫道：「隨著克拉克的不適感上升，保羅森演出的小細節使她更顯人性[…] 凡斯飾演的卡克倫有時搞笑，但他有著情緒上的流動，使他偶爾內斂的同時，亦顯得更加聰明。」<ref name="FeinbergHR" />〈[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]〉的布萊恩·勞瑞（{{lang|en|Brian Lowry}}）亦讚揚了{{link-en|康妮·布里登|Connie Britton}}與[[納坦·朗|奈森·連恩]]的表現。<ref name="LowryVariety">{{cite web|last1=Lowry|first1=Brian|title=TV Review: ‘The People v. O.J. Simpson: American Crime Story’|url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/reviews/the-people-v-o-j-simpson-american-crime-story-review-fx-john-travolta-cuba-gooding-jr-ryan-murphy-1201684402/|work=綜藝雜誌|date=2016-01-27|accessdate=2016-02-03|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130051137/https://variety.com/2016/tv/reviews/the-people-v-o-j-simpson-american-crime-story-review-fx-john-travolta-cuba-gooding-jr-ryan-murphy-1201684402/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

儘管其他演員獲得了讚賞，但[[約翰·特拉沃爾塔|約翰·屈伏塔]]與[[小庫珀·古丁|小古巴·古汀]]的演出卻獲得好壞參半的評價。〈綜藝雜誌〉的布萊恩·勞瑞表示：「沒錯，沙皮洛說話僵硬卻抑揚頓挫，但演員過分的矯飾台詞使得律師一角成了一名小丑，與其他演員細膩的演出有著鮮明的對比。」<ref name="LowryVariety"/>〈[[名利場_(雜誌)|浮華世界]]〉的妮可·瓊斯（{{lang|en|Nicole Jones}}）稱屈伏塔的表現「不自然又刻意」。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Jones|first1=Nicole|title=The People v. O.J. Simpson Recap: Episode 1 Fact Check|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/02/people-v-oj-simpson-episode-1-recap|work=[[名利場_(雜誌)|浮華世界]]|date=2016-02-02|accessdate=2016-02-03|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921040424/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/02/people-v-oj-simpson-episode-1-recap|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈好萊塢報導〉的丹·范伯格則稱其演出是「毫無吸引力的糟糕表現。」<ref name="FeinbergHR"/>

〈綜藝雜誌〉的莫琳·萊恩（{{lang|en|Maureen Ryan}}）隨著故事的推展，反而對屈伏塔有更深刻的印象：「我從一開始的困惑與懷疑，來到富有娛樂性，最終真誠的讚賞。你完全無法從約翰·屈伏塔身上移開視線，就像有著某種魔力一般。」<ref name="">{{cite web|last1=Ryan|first1=Maureen|title='In His High-Profile Return to TV, John Travolta Gets Noticed'|url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/opinion/john-travolta-the-people-v-oj-simpson-american-crime-story-1201695009/|work=綜藝雜誌|date=2016-02-10|accessdate=2016-03-15|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029103326/https://variety.com/2016/tv/opinion/john-travolta-the-people-v-oj-simpson-american-crime-story-1201695009/|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石雜誌]]〉的伊莉莎白·加伯-保羅（{{lang|en|Elisabeth Garber-Paul}}）稱道：「可以說是[屈伏塔]在[[昆汀·塔倫蒂諾|昆汀·塔倫蒂諾]][[低俗小說|讓他的演藝事業起死回生]]後最佳的一次演出。」<ref name="egp">{{cite news|last1=Garber-Paul|first1=Elisabeth|title='The People v. O.J. Simpson,' Episode 1: Our Fact-Checking Recap|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/recaps/the-people-v-o-j-simpson-episode-1-our-fact-checking-recap-20160202|accessdate=2016-06-02|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石雜誌]]|date=2016-02-03|archive-date=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228171530/https://www.rollingstone.com/tv/recaps/the-people-v-o-j-simpson-episode-1-our-fact-checking-recap-20160202|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈[[今日美國|今日美國]]〉的羅伯特·比安可（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）認為屈伏塔是節目中有著“表現最廣”的演員。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bianco|first1=Robert|title=Review: The glove fits; O.J. trial series guilty of 'stunning' performances|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/columnist/2016/02/01/review-glove-fits-stunning-portrayals-oj-simpson-trial-players/79510362/|accessdate=2016-06-02|work=[[今日美國|今日美國]]|date=2016-02-02|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807170701/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/columnist/2016/02/01/review-glove-fits-stunning-portrayals-oj-simpson-trial-players/79510362/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

〈[[衛報|衛報]]〉的戴夫·席林（{{lang|en|Dave Schilling}}） 評論古汀的演出：「他低估、沙啞的聲音聽起來與O·J·辛普森低沉、命令式口吻完全不像。」<ref name="The Guardian Review">{{cite web|last1=Schilling|first1=Dave|title=The People v OJ Simpson: episode one – great casting, with one exception|url=http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2016/feb/05/the-people-v-oj-simpson-casting-cuba-gooding-jr|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|accessdate=2016-08-05|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105084839/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2016/feb/05/the-people-v-oj-simpson-casting-cuba-gooding-jr|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈[[紐約郵報|紐約郵報]]〉的邁克爾·斯塔爾（{{lang|en|Michael Starr}}）亦強烈評論古汀的表現：「演繹辛普森為一個空洞、悲痛麻木與講話高分貝的人物，亦在遭逮捕後沒有絲毫的情感動搖。他是個不起眼又惱人的存在，就像只把台詞念出一樣，而他也只能做到這麼多。」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Starr|first1=Michael|title=Cuba Gooding Jr. has made despicable O.J. Simpson boring|url=http://nypost.com/2016/02/23/cuba-gooding-jr-has-made-despicable-o-j-simpson-boring/|work=[[紐約郵報|紐約郵報]]|accessdate=2016-04-03|archive-date=2020-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815002104/https://nypost.com/2016/02/23/cuba-gooding-jr-has-made-despicable-o-j-simpson-boring/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而古汀以本劇入圍[[第68屆黃金時段艾美獎|艾美獎]]一事，則遭到不少評論家的高度嘲諷。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Marcus|first1=Stephanie|title=Cuba Gooding Jr.’s Emmy Nomination For Playing O.J. Simpson Is Puzzling To Say The Least|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/cuba-gooding-jrs-emmy-nomination-for-playing-oj-simpson-is-puzzling_us_5787e40fe4b08608d3339db1?|work=[[赫芬頓郵報|赫芬頓郵報]]|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2017-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170405100206/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/cuba-gooding-jrs-emmy-nomination-for-playing-oj-simpson-is-puzzling_us_5787e40fe4b08608d3339db1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

